HEADWORD: Froebelian
<hw>Froe*bel"i*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to,
or derived from, Friedrich <etsep>Froebel</etsep>, or the kindergarten
system of education, which he organized.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos>
<def>One who teaches by, or advocates the use of, the kindergarten
system.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

